{"tid":814543,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"( 實試 ) 半島奶黃月餅其實唔係講到咁差","createTime":"2018-09-11T10:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T17:07:34.000Z","uid":45206,"like":19,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab6674392b7adc10ebd2b3cf2a31e28ba42bc1e","tid":814543,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"買盒試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/180950_0e4dd435e1fd11c37634ee53e5cd6a33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F180950_0e4dd435e1fd11c37634ee53e5cd6a33.png&h=cb0ea7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗外面個套 入面係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/181025_6ceb07676f5d66f6a56c2ed0a4a6ac49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F181025_6ceb07676f5d66f6a56c2ed0a4a6ac49.png&h=8097400b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又再打開一層 有張牛油紙 話食之前要焗6分鐘 或者叮15秒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/181153_d925785e6308dd56996ecfd14473226b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F181153_d925785e6308dd56996ecfd14473226b.png&h=442fa793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未入焗爐之前係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/181226_dd8207c6272638cf3ee6714b126d9144.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F181226_dd8207c6272638cf3ee6714b126d9144.png&h=f6c2466e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween個盒設計得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/181327_ea7fc2a6983c071ebf385ec6f39e340a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F181327_ea7fc2a6983c071ebf385ec6f39e340a.png&h=cdb253af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/175751_0720f7cf107f74482e24f37607cc98dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F175751_0720f7cf107f74482e24f37607cc98dd.png&h=b3809bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n焗完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/175834_699b1d97fd2ae42b7d3beb15dd4022a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F175834_699b1d97fd2ae42b7d3beb15dd4022a3.png&h=5805a121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切開咁樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/180011_207168f0882809bb767d1a0cf6b354f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F180011_207168f0882809bb767d1a0cf6b354f7.png&h=a13b1412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實味道無之前連登仔講咁差<br />\n個皮好酥脆 而且幾香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就一定要焗 / 叮過 試過室溫食係勁甜勁大油味<br />\n流心就流唔到 但講真係幾好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58c42ee49b42b1c52d58dd2609f291c60ce3599","tid":814543,"uid":208726,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87734f47c5dcbc16a675d811df5e5bf0d5e9e23e","tid":814543,"uid":45206,"like":19,"dislike":2,"s